# Cursor Rules — Darling MarTech (Minimal)

## Read first

- AGENT_SYSTEM.md
- docs/agent/*

These are the canonical instructions.

---

## Core behavior

- Make small, scoped changes
- Do not modify unrelated files
- Prefer repo reality over docs when they conflict
- Follow problem-first architecture
- Keep solo-operator voice intact

---

## Validation

Before completion:
- pnpm typecheck
- pnpm build (if page/runtime changed)

---

## Do not

- introduce generic agency language
- rewrite large sections without reason
- add dependencies casually
- break routing or data model consistency

---

## Goal

Improve the system incrementally while preserving structure, clarity, and conversion logic.
